But it is so much better than perfect,
because...

34:05.376 --> 34:06.210
it's real.

34:09.589 --> 34:10.923
Wait. Wait, I want to go.

34:11.549 --> 34:12.592
Forty...

34:12.675 --> 34:14.093
No, I want to go. I want to go.

34:15.636 --> 34:17.472
Um...

34:17.805 --> 34:19.891
-Forty?
- Um, remember...

34:20.308 --> 34:22.935
when they, uh, they dragged us
to the Hoffman Institute

34:23.019 --> 34:25.396
because, uh,
they had differing definitions

34:25.480 --> 34:26.939
of the word "monogamish"?

34:27.023 --> 34:29.108
-That was real.

34:29.192 --> 34:30.651
-I have more. I just, uh--
-Enough, son.

34:30.735 --> 34:32.445
I-- I just need a smoke.

34:32.862 --> 34:34.489
Just need a smoke.

34:34.572 --> 34:37.784
Oh, um, not that one. No, it's fine.
It's-- it's okay. Got it. It's okay.

34:37.867 --> 34:38.868
- It's okay.
-Oh!

34:39.952 --> 34:41.287
It's fine. Everything's...

34:41.829 --> 34:42.914
You look lovely, Mom.

34:43.706 --> 34:44.749
Let's go. It's okay. Shh.

34:44.832 --> 34:46.459
-I don't feel good.
- Yeah.

34:47.085 --> 34:47.919
I do.

34:50.421 --> 34:51.464
Let's party!

34:57.970 --> 34:59.222
Hey. Hey, hey, hey.

34:59.639 --> 35:01.516
-How are you guys doing?
-You've done enough.

35:01.891 --> 35:04.769
All you ever have to do
is keep your brother safe. You failed.

35:05.603 --> 35:06.729
You disgust me.

35:13.778 --> 35:15.029
You're a fucking hypocrite.

35:20.409 --> 35:21.577
<i> Earth mommy dearest.</i>

35:21.911 --> 35:22.912
<i>Oh, Love.</i>

35:26.040 --> 35:28.376
It's okay, it's okay. It's okay.

35:29.377 --> 35:30.419
-It's okay.

35:31.671 --> 35:32.630
It's okay.

35:36.467 --> 35:39.262
<i> I saw what your mom did.</i>
<i>Are you okay?</i>

35:42.807 --> 35:44.225
My dad hit me a lot.

35:49.147 --> 35:50.398
Why couldn't you tell me?

35:51.482 --> 35:53.693
Probably...
same reason you couldn't tell me.

35:53.985 --> 35:56.821
I couldn't tell you
because I wanted us to stay us.

35:57.864 --> 36:00.867
I didn't want it to be polluted
by all this fucking...

36:04.078 --> 36:04.954
I guess...

36:07.665 --> 36:09.000
my life has been dark.

36:10.376 --> 36:12.378
Well, who you really are...

36:13.129 --> 36:15.006
the dark, that's not a burden.

36:15.089 --> 36:16.883
You don't have to push that away from me.

36:18.551 --> 36:19.760
I want to know you.

36:21.804 --> 36:23.014
I want to know you.

36:23.097 --> 36:25.516
You know, the more I get to know you,
the nicer it is.

36:26.559 --> 36:28.102
I don't just mean the cute parts.

36:30.229 --> 36:31.439
As far as I'm concerned...

36:32.982 --> 36:34.358
we will stay us...

36:35.860 --> 36:36.777
no matter what.

36:40.531 --> 36:43.618
Yeah, I feel like I've been, um...
I've been acting weird,

36:43.701 --> 36:45.745
and I feel like it's because
there's all these things

36:45.828 --> 36:48.748
that I felt like I couldn't tell you,
but, like, fuck that.

36:51.250 --> 36:52.835
Okay, um...

36:54.420 --> 36:55.963
You remember the, um...

36:57.965 --> 37:00.301
the Nilla Wafers, the <i>au pair?</i>

37:00.968 --> 37:01.802
Of course.

37:01.886 --> 37:03.638
My parents started Anavrin

37:03.721 --> 37:05.097
when we were, like, 13.

37:07.016 --> 37:10.019
And they hired this woman, Sofia.

37:10.353 --> 37:12.772
She was, like, 19. She was from Spain.

37:15.733 --> 37:17.026
The way Forty tells it...

37:18.194 --> 37:20.321
she was his first love.

37:20.529 --> 37:22.240
To this day, he does not acknowledge

37:22.323 --> 37:24.909
that it was was abuse.

37:28.329 --> 37:31.624
And eventually my parents
caught them together,

37:32.208 --> 37:33.042
and...

37:33.793 --> 37:35.711
so much shit ensued.

37:37.213 --> 37:39.131
And... they let her go.

37:40.508 --> 37:42.343
And she was troubled.

37:43.844 --> 37:44.887
She killed herself.

37:48.432 --> 37:50.184
Forty's the one who found the body.

37:53.813 --> 37:55.856
Yeah, and nothing has ever
really been the same.

37:57.441 --> 37:59.860
My parents kept everything quiet
with money.

38:03.781 --> 38:04.824
Yeah.

38:05.533 --> 38:08.452
I get that Forty is a lot. I know.

38:12.039 --> 38:14.250
And I know
that I take care of him too much.

38:16.127 --> 38:17.003
But...

38:18.129 --> 38:20.423
you've met my parents now,
so you know why.

38:21.549 --> 38:22.508
I'm stuck with him.

38:22.591 --> 38:23.426
No.

38:24.218 --> 38:25.219
<i>We</i> are.

38:31.892 --> 38:34.353
<i> I don't think</i>
<i>I've ever been in love before.</i>

38:36.814 --> 38:39.900
<i>-It's been infatuation.</i>

38:40.943 --> 38:42.903
<i>This is it.</i>

38:43.279 --> 38:46.490
<i>Accepting you're not perfect</i>
<i>and loving you more for it.</i>

38:57.209 --> 38:58.377
What the fuck?

39:05.009 --> 39:06.469
I'm sorry, did that trigger you?

39:21.067 --> 39:22.777
Can I tell you I love you yet?

39:27.406 --> 39:28.282
Whenever you're ready.

39:33.371 --> 39:34.872
In the meantime, let me say...

39:36.624 --> 39:37.792
I love you...

39:38.292 --> 39:39.126
Love.

39:41.128 --> 39:43.297
Ugh, it's a complicated word.

39:44.715 --> 39:45.966
Oh, yeah.

39:46.050 --> 39:48.010
Is there another word we can use?
Our word?

39:48.969 --> 39:49.887
Um...

39:52.181 --> 39:53.432
I wolf you.

39:55.267 --> 39:56.352
I wolf you too.

40:00.064 --> 40:01.065
I like it.

40:02.191 --> 40:03.859
It's like you're part of my pack.

40:06.237 --> 40:07.238
I am your pack.

40:34.098 --> 40:35.516
-Hey!
-Klepto.

40:35.599 --> 40:37.101
The police came for these.

40:37.184 --> 40:39.770
-The actual police or your fuckboy?
-Why would you take these?

40:42.565 --> 40:44.108
I couldn't believe he would do this.

40:48.195 --> 40:49.029
But I do now.

40:52.950 --> 40:55.244
I'm sorry I was being such an asshole.

40:57.246 --> 40:58.164
It's okay.

41:02.042 --> 41:03.544
I think we should burn those.

41:04.670 --> 41:06.505
If these photos were ever leaked...

41:07.089 --> 41:09.258
every time someone googled the girls,

41:09.341 --> 41:10.384
it would just...

41:13.387 --> 41:14.930
What would you want done with yours?

41:18.350 --> 41:19.351
Hey, just so you know...

41:21.437 --> 41:24.148
nothing could ever
make me see you different.

41:41.749 --> 41:43.167
<i>Tell me again what happened.</i>

41:43.834 --> 41:46.629
Um, my boyfriend... ex...

41:47.129 --> 41:48.005
We fought.

41:48.422 --> 41:50.174
And he...

41:50.841 --> 41:52.259
He took me to the woods.

41:52.510 --> 41:53.427
Um...

41:54.512 --> 41:56.347
I don't remember what happened next.

41:57.223 --> 41:58.599
I just... I-- I woke up.

41:59.558 --> 42:00.392
Like...

42:02.019 --> 42:02.978
buried.

42:04.480 --> 42:06.774
We sent a car out. No tire marks.

42:06.857 --> 42:08.025
No, he dug a grave.

42:09.443 --> 42:12.154
A lot of tree removal in that area, right?
Loose dirt.

42:12.655 --> 42:13.697
No one saw anything?

42:14.698 --> 42:17.326
You happen to take any pictures
or save any texts between you?

42:17.409 --> 42:18.327
No!

42:18.786 --> 42:20.454
He has my phone!

42:20.996 --> 42:23.541
I mean, isn't there any DNA
where he buried me alive?

42:23.624 --> 42:26.293
This isn't <i>CSI,</i> all right?
We're in Putnam County.

42:27.461 --> 42:29.380
So you have no proof?

42:34.843 --> 42:37.888
Honey, let me level with you, all right?

42:38.472 --> 42:39.306
I looked you up.

42:39.807 --> 42:41.475
-You have a rap sheet.

42:41.725 --> 42:44.061
Ever had any friends go through
with reporting assault?

42:46.230 --> 42:47.731
This'll be labeled domestic violence.

42:47.815 --> 42:49.108
This isn't--

42:50.150 --> 42:52.444
He tried to murder me.

42:52.695 --> 42:55.739
The best we can do
is get a restraining order.

42:55.864 --> 42:57.157
Right, temp for three months.

42:57.241 --> 42:59.285
For a permanent one,
you'll have to stand before a judge,

42:59.410 --> 43:01.203
-so will he.
-But it will be permanent?

43:01.287 --> 43:02.997
Well, three years.

43:03.080 --> 43:04.331
And then file again.

43:04.415 --> 43:06.792
If you have no pics, no proof...

43:09.420 --> 43:11.130
What am I supposed to do?

43:20.014 --> 43:21.223
He thinks you're dead?

43:21.849 --> 43:24.226
You want some really
off-the-record advice?

43:25.352 --> 43:26.312
Stay that way.

43:31.233 --> 43:32.526
This is unreal.

43:42.953 --> 43:44.204
Figured you'd come find me.

43:50.377 --> 43:53.464
Crazy family
we've fallen into, huh?

43:55.132 --> 43:56.133
So now you see I'm not--

43:56.383 --> 43:58.052
I'm not afraid of you anymore.

43:59.762 --> 44:01.930
If you really had something on me...

44:03.849 --> 44:07.019
-you would've turned me in already.
-I'm not afraid of you either.

44:07.394 --> 44:08.687
Why would you be afraid of me?

44:09.772 --> 44:10.981
Candace, it was an accident.

44:13.233 --> 44:14.234
End of story.

44:18.280 --> 44:19.365
I never tried to kill you.

44:19.448 --> 44:21.617
Yeah. You know what they say?

44:22.326 --> 44:25.829
You never know if you're fight or flight
until you're forced to find out.

44:26.205 --> 44:27.206
Turns out...

44:29.500 --> 44:30.417
I'm fight.

44:32.586 --> 44:34.338
So now I found you,

44:34.421 --> 44:36.298
I'm not going anywhere,

44:36.382 --> 44:39.343
and I don't care what story
you tell yourself,

44:39.426 --> 44:42.388
because all I have to do
is wait for you to mess up.

44:45.265 --> 44:47.142
Murder has a way of following you.

44:48.060 --> 44:49.687
And you're not getting away with it.

45:06.245 --> 45:08.205
<i>Things aren't over with Candace.</i>

45:08.997 --> 45:12.543
<i>But I have to rest</i>
<i>before I plan my next move.</i>

45:12.918 --> 45:14.420
<i>Wellness is exhausting.</i>

45:19.466 --> 45:20.300
<i>Huh.</i>

45:20.926 --> 45:23.011
<i>A postcard from Will in Manila.</i>

45:23.512 --> 45:25.055
<i>It's going well with Gigi.</i>

45:26.098 --> 45:28.642
<i>If I stay committed to being a good man,</i>

45:28.976 --> 45:30.769
<i>things might work themselves out.</i>

45:31.061 --> 45:33.105
My God, why aren't they burning?

45:33.188 --> 45:34.815
We need kindling.

45:35.691 --> 45:36.984
Oh, man.

45:38.152 --> 45:40.404
Evidently, there's toxins in Polaroids.

45:48.871 --> 45:50.080
All right, there's one more.

46:30.454 --> 46:32.331
-Aw.
-I wolf you.

46:32.581 --> 46:33.791
Mm. Do you now?

46:33.874 --> 46:35.042
-Yeah.

46:40.464 --> 46:41.840
Do you want to go to the stockroom?

46:41.924 --> 46:43.675
Yes, I would like that very much.

46:47.012 --> 46:48.430
Stop with the PDA.

46:50.432 --> 46:52.351
Before anybody asks...

46:52.643 --> 46:54.686
Amy picked me up from a meeting,

46:54.770 --> 46:56.396
where I found a new sponsor.

46:56.480 --> 46:58.273
Can't name names, but, uh...

46:58.357 --> 47:00.818
-let's just say the Academy robbed him.

47:00.901 --> 47:03.862
Anyway, I will have to make amends.

47:03.946 --> 47:06.490
So I promise I will apologize
to both of you...

47:07.157 --> 47:08.909
whenever I get to that step.

47:08.992 --> 47:10.369
You don't need to do that.

47:11.578 --> 47:12.913
I'm just glad you're okay.

47:14.039 --> 47:17.084
I really am.
And, um, I'm staying busy too.

47:17.167 --> 47:21.338
I mean... adapting this book
Amy found for us is going to consume me,

47:21.839 --> 47:23.757
in the best way possible.

47:24.216 --> 47:26.426
-Thank fuck we got that option.

47:26.802 --> 47:27.845
What's the book?

47:27.928 --> 47:31.056
I thought you were busy prepping
<i>Bang, Marry, Kill.</i>

47:31.139 --> 47:33.600
Yeah, that felt like more
of a second feature.

47:33.684 --> 47:36.061
But, uh...
Amy turned me on to this memoir.

47:39.690 --> 47:42.276
Yeah, this main character, Beck...

47:42.609 --> 47:44.570
she really speaks to me, you know?

47:45.153 --> 47:47.155
-She just wanted to be loved.
- Mm.

47:47.239 --> 47:50.784
-<i> She's worse than Eva Braun.</i>
-Oh! Ugh!

47:50.909 --> 47:53.328
Anyway, just waiting for the deal points
to come through, but--

47:53.412 --> 47:55.247
- Oh, my God.

47:58.584 --> 47:59.543
Holy fuck.

48:00.168 --> 48:01.503
-No way.
-What?

48:01.587 --> 48:02.796
- Hold on.
-What happened?

48:02.880 --> 48:03.755
No way.

48:04.840 --> 48:07.134
Now they're saying
they think Henderson was murdered.

48:09.094 --> 48:12.055
<i> Benji, Peach, Beck,</i>
<i>Ron, Jasper, Henderson...</i>

48:12.848 --> 48:15.809
Well, if-- if that's true,
a famous man like Henderson,

48:15.893 --> 48:18.186
they won't stop
until they find who did it, right?

48:18.270 --> 48:20.022
-Right.
-He won't get away with it.

48:23.692 --> 48:25.402
Murder has a way of following you.

